                <html:p>If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(X,d)]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="/ca-001T/" title="Compact subset of a metric space" uri="http://localhost:8000/ca-001T/" display-uri="ca-001T" type="local">compact</fr:link> <fr:link href="/ca-000K/" title="Metric Space" uri="http://localhost:8000/ca-000K/" display-uri="ca-000K" type="local">Metric Space</fr:link>, then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}(X)]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/ca-001F/" title="Complete Metric Space" uri="http://localhost:8000/ca-001F/" display-uri="ca-001F" type="local">complete</fr:link>.</html:p>
